t\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\resources\\gutter-red.svg       \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\walkthrough\\codeAction.svg     \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\walkthrough\\debugAndTest.svg   \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\walkthrough\\extensions.svg     \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\walkthrough\\helpCenter.svg     \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\walkthrough\\helpCenterMac.svg  \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\walkthrough\\ok.svg             \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\walkthrough\\projects.svg       \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\walkthrough\\runtime.md         \r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\webview-resources\\highlight.css\r\nC:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.antigravity-ide\\extensions\\vscjava.vscode-java-pack-0.31.1-universal\\webview-resources\\java-forma...\r\n\r\n\r\n",
